n-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<p>여러 다른 인터페이스도 CSSOM-related 규격에 의해 확장됩니다 :&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLImageElement\"><code>HTMLImageElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_typed_object_model","title":"CSS 자료형 객체 모델&nbsp;<svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg>","isH3":true,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"index\" id=\"